Package: LobsterCatch
Title: Models capture processes in American lobster trap fishery
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Pourfaraj", "vahab", , "vpourfaraj@gmail.com", role = c("aut","cre")),
    person("Cook", "Adam", , "Adam.Cook@dfo-mpo.gc.ca", role = c("aut")),
    person("Jamie", "Tam", , "Jamie.Tam@dfo-mpo.gc.ca", role = "ctb"),
    person("Nickchi", "Payman", , "payman.nickchi@gmail.com", role = c("aut"))
  )
Description: Functions to simulate lobster catch process in a trap fishery. Factors such as lobsters behavior, their size and sex as well as bait shrinkage rate can be modeled using the package.
